{"content": "I need to multiply 101 \u00d7 658 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n101\u2089 = 1\u00d79\u00b2 + 0\u00d79\u00b9 + 1\u00d79\u2070 = 81 + 0 + 1 = 82\u2081\u2080\n\n658\u2089 = 6\u00d79\u00b2 + 5\u00d79\u00b9 + 8\u00d79\u2070 = 6\u00d781 + 5\u00d79 + 8\u00d71 = 486 + 45 + 8 = 539\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n82 \u00d7 539 = 44,198\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n44198 \u00f7 9 = 4910 r 8\n4910 \u00f7 9 = 545 r 5\n545 \u00f7 9 = 60 r 5\n60 \u00f7 9 = 6 r 6\n6 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 6\n\nReading from bottom to top: 66558\u2089\n\n**Step 4: Verification**\n\n66558\u2089 = 6\u00d79\u2074 + 6\u00d79\u00b3 + 5\u00d79\u00b2 + 5\u00d79\u00b9 + 8\u00d79\u2070\n= 6\u00d76561 + 6\u00d7729 + 5\u00d781 + 5\u00d79 + 8\u00d71\n= 39366 + 4374 + 405 + 45 + 8\n= 44198\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n66558", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1150, "completion_tokens": 407}